  "implementationSummary": "Added public GET /v1/auth/tiktok/business/account-holder/callback for TikTok Business account-holder OAuth: validates auth_code+state, exchanges via business-api.tiktok.com v1.3 oauth2/access_token/, persists encrypted credentials with capability business_account_holder separate from Shop and Advertiser rows, and mirrors Shop callback error semantics (400/401/502/503).",
  "assumptions": [
    "TikTok Business account-holder redirect uses query param auth_code (Marketing API) and the same POST /open_api/v1.3/oauth2/access_token/ endpoint as advertiser/creator flows.",
    "Token subject key is creator_id when present; merchant_authorization_id stores that value with capability business_account_holder.",
    "Env: TIKTOK_BUSINESS_APP_ID, TIKTOK_BUSINESS_APP_SECRET, TIKTOK_BUSINESS_ACCOUNT_HOLDER_REDIRECT_URI (redirect URI used at auth initiation; not required for callback handler)."
  ],
